<font  face="times new roman"><b><a href="http://www.nytimes.com/2001/11/22/nyregion/22MIKE.html?todaysheadlines">Developer Briefs Bloomberg on Plans to Rebuild Towers</a></b><br>
Larry A. Silverstein, the developer who holds the lease on the World Trade Center, met with Mayor-elect Michael R. Bloomberg and said that he would go ahead with plans to rebuild at the site.
<P>
</font>













